name: "Cherry Blossoms (Animated MP4)" By Sunny Crittenden
description: "Cherry Blossoms (Animated MP4)" was created in May 2020. It was the 2nd piece the artist ever created on her iPad inherited from her husband, with a 2nd hand Apple Pencil donated by a patron, using Procreate, and was the first of her signature SunnyGrrrls to be drawn digitally. It is also the 1st animation the artist ever did in her whole life. "Cherry Blossoms" is essentially SunnyGrrrls' digital genesis.
